        <![CDATA[
        <h1>About</h1>

        <p>A simple app to view the daily menus for the dining courts at Purdue University. This app
        is open source. Pull requests are welcome.</p>

        <p><a href="https://github.com/sargunster/purdue-dining-courts-android">View on Github</a></p>
        <p><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=me.sargunvohra.android.purduediningcourts">View on Play Store</a></p>

        <h1>API</h1>
        <p>This app uses the Purdue dining menus API. Information on this API can be found on <a href="http://tyhoffman.com/blog/2013/04/purdue-dining-court-api/">this page</a>.</p>

